  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Brutalismus: Chapter 1 is a short Brutalism inspired first person walking simulator, atmospheric exploration experience.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2833840/extras/17815ae24de3d4aaab9fc6a607a2e31f.avif?t=1765985275\" width=616 height=92 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Where The air is thick with an eerie silence, enjoy the comfort of the safe rooms,    <br>and find a way trough the unknown.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover strange notes, and feel the empty atmosphere.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Prepare for the unforeseen consequences... and well also   <br>sometimes you may be left wondering, who is Lily?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2833840/extras/200ee4e22b2acb315b95c6b8e55ea1e7.avif?t=1765985275\" width=616 height=92 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Developed by an independent one man studio from Croatia.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>           <i>Induction Studio</i></strong></p>",
